column1: Honoring Our Veterans
column3: Today marks the 103rd anniversary of the armistice that ended the First World War. November 11th has since become an international day for honoring men and women who served their countries' armed forces. Whether you are celebrating Veterans Day, Armistice Day, or Remembrance Day today, we at BaT will also be thinking of the millions of people who have given so much to all of us through their service.
